OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773943560
OL,3,CKate Quilton reports on whether
OL,4,Cloyalty schemes and in-store discounts
OL,5,Cdeliver.
OL,7,FIn this week's episode of Tonight, we
OL,8,Flook at some of the ways shoppers can
OL,9,Fcut the cost of their food bill.
OL,10,FReporter Kate Quilton does a typical
OL,11,Fmid-week shop while wearing specialist
OL,12,Feye-tracking technology, with
OL,13,Fbehavioural expert Will Morgan and
OL,14,Fretail psychologist Phillip Adcock
OL,15,Fable to analyse what products grab her
OL,16,Fattention and how the layout of the
OL,17,Fshop influences her choices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
