FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773943560
OL,3,CKate Quilton reports on whether
OL,4,Cloyalty schemes and in-store discounts
OL,5,Cdeliver.
OL,7,FWhen asked his top tips on how
OL,8,Fshoppers can knock some money off
OL,9,Ftheir food bills, Phillip said: "Don't
OL,10,Fshop tired, don't shop hungry, and
OL,11,Fdon't just grab it off the fixture and
OL,12,Fthink 'oh it's got a red label, it
OL,13,Fmust be a special offer."
OL,26,@qD@aOUuD@YO]
