OL,3,CKate Quilton reports on whether
OL,4,Cloyalty schemes and in-store discounts
OL,5,Cdeliver.
OL,7,FAccording to a survey, 97% of shoppers
OL,8,Fare a member of at least one
OL,9,Fsupermarket loyalty scheme. For super
OL,10,Fsaver Samantha, who has gained
OL,11,Fthousands of online followers by
OL,12,Fsharing her advice, loyalty schemes
OL,13,Fcan help us save on our food bill but
OL,14,Fsays they are not the only thing to
OL,15,Fconsider. Another recommendation
OL,16,FSamantha shares is to look at
OL,17,Fsupermarket own brand and budget
OL,18,Franges.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
