OL,3,CKate Quilton reports on whether
OL,4,Cloyalty schemes and in-store discounts
OL,5,Cdeliver.
OL,7,FRetail analyst Fraser McKevitt adds:
OL,8,F"Prices are rising across most of the
OL,9,Fshelves in the supermarket, but there
OL,10,Fare a few that stand out. So fresh
OL,11,Fmeat in particular is going up in
OL,12,Fdouble digit rate, and all throughout
OL,13,Fthe last year, the price of chocolate
OL,14,Fhas been going up very, very sharply
OL,15,Fas well, and I think you'll start to
OL,16,Fsee that effect when you look to buy
OL,17,Fyour Easter eggs."
OL,26,@pD@AOUyD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
