CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773943560
OL,3,CKate Quilton reports on whether
OL,4,Cloyalty schemes and in-store discounts
OL,5,Cdeliver.
OL,7,FTonight also spoke to Edwina Dunn, who
OL,8,Fhelped pioneer Tesco's Clubcard, which
OL,9,Flaunched in 1995. She said: "The idea
OL,10,Fwas to track what people bought, give
OL,11,Fthem a 1% reward, and then work out
OL,12,Fwhat they loved, to try and
OL,13,Fincentivise them to say 'Oh Tesco
OL,14,Frecognises I like this, they've given
OL,15,Fme an extra coupon, an extra promotion
OL,16,Fto always come back to them and buy
OL,17,Fthat'." From the very beginning, data
OL,18,Fcollection was central. But the idea
OL,19,Fof two-tier pricing in supermarkets
OL,20,Fcame later, meaning shoppers were
OL,21,Fobliged to have a loyalty card in
OL,22,Forder to access the cheaper pricing.
OL,26,@qD@]OUyD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
