OL,3,CKate Quilton reports on whether
OL,4,Cloyalty schemes and in-store discounts
OL,5,Cdeliver.
OL,7,FAlmost 40% of us say we are
OL,8,Funcomfortable with the amount of data
OL,9,Fsupermarkets collect. Tesco told
OL,10,FTonight that it is transparent about
OL,11,Fthe way they use customer data, and
OL,12,Fthat "the data that customers share
OL,13,Fwith us is used to personalise
OL,14,Foffers...". Tesco said: "We do not
OL,15,Fsell any data we collect from
OL,16,Fcustomers to third parties."
OL,26,@tD@FOUvD@JO]vD@YOUxD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
