OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773943560
OL,3,CKate Quilton reports on whether
OL,4,Cloyalty schemes and in-store discounts
OL,5,Cdeliver.
OL,7,FAnd in 2019, Dr James Flanagan began a
OL,8,Fgroundbreaking study aimed at using
OL,9,Fshopping data to help diagnose serious
OL,10,Fillness long before patients first
OL,11,Fvisit the GP. His first study focused
OL,12,Fon patients with ovarian cancer,
OL,13,Flooking back at their shopping history
OL,14,Fto find changes in shopping behaviour
OL,15,Fthat might be a clue to a person
OL,16,Fhaving the disease.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773943560
OL,3,CKate Quilton reports on whether
OL,4,Cloyalty schemes and in-store discounts
OL,5,Cdeliver.
OL,7,F"The ovarian cancer patients were
OL,8,Fbuying products like Gaviscon pain
OL,9,Fmedication to treat their symptoms
OL,10,Fabout eight or nine months before
OL,11,Ftheir diagnosis, and this was about
OL,12,Fthree or four months before they would
OL,13,Factually go to the GP for the first
OL,14,Ftime," Dr Flanagan told Tonight.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@FO]
