OL,7,FThey are now looking ahead to a future
OL,8,Fin which we could consent for our
OL,9,Fshopping data to be used to give early
OL,10,Findications that we should visit a GP-
OL,11,F showing loyalty cards are continuing
OL,12,Fto evolve, in sometimes unexpected
OL,13,Fways.
